                                <td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td><a href="viewtopic.php?p=56636&amp;sid=9b6b7d892414a2918fa1943ba06688f6#56636"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Wed Jul 14, 2004 12:43 pm<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: Enchanter Class Description (make your own)</span></td>
                                <td align="right" valign="top" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=56636&amp;sid=9b6b7d892414a2918fa1943ba06688f6"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>    </td></tr></table></td>
