                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"><span style="font-style: italic">Enchanters are not the most direct class, everything they do is to influence those around them.  They are considered a force multiplier.  They greatly enhance the combat abilities of their melee friends through haste spells and effects, while at the same time significantly increasing the mana pools and regen of their spellcasting comrades.  While they refrain from directly entering combat, when they do it is always a sight to see.  An enchanter will rush into a thick crowd of monsters and swirling chaos, and then for a brief instant, bring order mesmerizing and slowing the attacks of the enemy and in some cases confusing the enemy to such a point that they change sides and help the enchanter and his friends.  Enchanters can be very persuasive and personable, add this to their illusion and faction abilities and they are a very commanding presence on and off the battlefield.</span>
<br />

<br />
------------------
<br />
Enchanters should be: 
<br />

<br />
<span style="color: darkblue">THE BEST </span>at crowd control, with an advantage not only in duration but in resists over other classes with mez
<br />

<br />
<span style="color: darkblue">THE BEST </span>at charm, highest resist check, longest duration, and highest level cap
<br />

<br />
<span style="color: darkblue">THE BEST </span>with illusions and faction and trickery, even if these means adding in a few more stealth type abilities or deagro ones, and bringing back faction and illusions
<br />

<br />
Among the best at buffs, be it haste/clarity/attack buffs etc
<br />

<br />
should avoid agro and damage v. mitigating it
<br />

<br />

<br />
<span style="color: green">NEED</span> more raid stackability, why with a 54 person cap should you bring another enchanter v. another wizard or cleric?
<br />

<br />
<span style="color: red">WANT</span> combination buffs, deception, a way to lose agro, and a way to mantain it</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=259328" target="_blank" class="postlink"><img src="http://www.therunes.net/forums/files/nanyea.gif" border="0" /></a>
<br />
<span style="color: cyan">EQ2 Area Moderator</span>
<br />
<a href="http://www.TheRunes.Net" target="_blank">www.TheRunes.Net</a>
<br />

<br />
