                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"><span style="font-style: italic">Enchanters are the most well-rounded of all the caster classes. They can improve the attack speed and mana regeneration to those around them, and eliminate chaos in any situation. They are the true masters of deception in Norrath, and use a variety of illusions and other spells to travel safely from place to place. Individually, they are a force to be reckoned with, but take many risks in achieving the desired rewards. They are a class that no group should be without, for they also add a greater chance of survivability through the uses of crowd control.</span></span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=273350" target="_blank" class="postlink">Mistress Senilea Starbreeze</a>
